Sarit Centre organised a Men Wellness initiative to celebrate Fathers' day on Sunday. Media personality Eddy Kimani was a guest speaker, giving men talk to fathers who attended the function. Fathers got treats from celebrity barbershop Barberia Cuts, Shami Beauty, Ashley's Furniture, Haier and Kashmir and Barista and Co. The men were celebrated with giveaways from Hotpoint, Newscafe, Beauty Quest, Roro's, Basco Paints and Swawosrki. The event happened at Sarit Centre in Westlands, Nairobi.